{"type": "article", "id": 33358, "title": "上海时装周继续更新，以及，东京有个卡地亚展值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-16T02:32:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 33826, "name": "2016 上海时装周"}, {"id": 33980, "name": "东京珠宝展"}, {"id": 33981, "name": "免税品市场"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 9472, "name": "Colette"}, {"id": 20300, "name": "Asics Tiger"}, {"id": 29000, "name": "Ted Baker"}, {"id": 33982, "name": "Chelsea"}, {"id": 33983, "name": "Emma Stone"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/201610161008494qoRC876wHfbZpQG.png", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.theindustrylondon.com/ted-baker-profits-surge-20-challenging-market/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>英国轻奢品牌 Ted Baker 上半年收入大涨</b></a> | 截止至 8 月 13 日，上半年 28 个周内，Ted Baker 的税前利润上涨了 20.5%，至 2150 万英镑。营业额则上涨了 14.4%，至 2.595 亿英镑。其中，北美地区上涨幅度最大，为 28.7%。Ted Baker 创立于 1988 年，它主打英伦风，除英国以外，在全球已有 195 家门店。&nbsp;<br></p><p><a href=\"https://jingdaily.com/chinese-shoppers-to-make-asia-surpass-europe-for-duty-free-market-share-by-2020/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>在中国消费者的推动下，亚洲免税品市场在 2020 年之前超过欧洲</b></a> | 据零售业分析机构 Verdict Retail 的报告指出，在 2015 年至 2020 年之间，全球免税品市场将产生 178 亿美元的销售额，其中有一半都来自于亚太地区。在接下来的四年内，全球免税品市场将平均每年以 6.7％ 的速度增长，得益于中国消费者庞大的购买力，亚洲地区的增幅最快，预计在 2020 年之前会超过欧洲市场。&nbsp;</p><h3>继续更新上海时装周：</h3><p class=\"\">Just in Case 2017 春夏系列灵感来自于西游记的「到此一游」，据说“将西方叛逆精神的朋克风与象征温婉的传统中国风相结合”，不过你也就这样一听就好了。</p><p>          </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002236y71AfI0vepPTDalu.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002237V2YCF7fem9HaI5zq.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002237f7lz1eu0iWSkYGJw.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002238OYv7Dqye4kXxgubR.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101600224198jIy4cL6g7bKlqT.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002242X0MR74Js5lCq3ohz.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002246qfAeFG7laUpwWENz.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002248UDhFVRPSwIEgzLJb.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499788\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002248HKyzgONJDWFvmA8s.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499567\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002249mE7qPfLlkuJvKY3h.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500211\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002252wKqXGRtFHdOUmiQE.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499782\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016002252ZG96vz4YsKJeowjk.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499546\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">TINA GIA 2017 春夏系列以 “生如夏花” 为主题，灵感来源于原始自然的民族文化。以手工编织工艺和标志性的民族细节来传递民族文化。</p><p>          </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232225RjBc6LW0lxHXbist.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232227J9M0Ri2lmtwc8TZj.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500460\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232227u5HOqazpoBh3kFVP.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500428\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232230Z2sfNW7OJMkPUb81.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232233BDZ4CMxAyK2v1wqm.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499760\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232233xcdtYBFVMWoHbvO2.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500224\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232232kxMEejrnaTA78KtX.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500210\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232239mPNjElgyLqnFO9Wf.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101523223947M1s20YSwUDNlO6.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499773\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610152322406csveXfzO0IRkGwg.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015232239rDgsCE5bBkdzc123.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">独立设计师品牌 REINEREN 本季以“POST OFFICE”邮局为灵感，邮票、邮戳以及包裹等元素都成为了这季的亮点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003815Ce7m02jzX9W8QxUu.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101600381608lAToiJFyHzekLf.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610160038165kwLGxetInqMJ0vV.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003817ldtZHjQYhNkJKw8e.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003824PzmSloucGtygrVUR.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003824N4KP9DYJWhzvIUuC.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003824UhZwy8FRxGTQ1AWb.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003825cwroIhgOpnmRMqV9.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500210\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003830yjSzHLceQiKgOk2b.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500675\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003832JW4gTZoNykfQOcuv.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003833KC5pGUzlycOYVtaR.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500210\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003835la6osm8GKn9SDRId.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003835OpnV2gEvtUAHYiC6.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499784\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Kids Wear 童装专场在时装周第三日亮点不断。LittleMee 希望表现孩子眼中的“欢乐”和“童真”。</p><p>          </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003913aiyVDReru6qIhsNf.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610160039137fb68CutY9Wa31qO.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003913aGq8N6IfViBkMdgJ.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003914ZQFo0xLOPkRV8sAT.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101600391535Y2P6odvusEUkaV.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003915SVUyO0cwh1tz9NrT.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003916soZVUl83RSfj5bPh.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003916Xm6elFNtxAQdoIUv.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003917Cczl5BjpNUQyGOe9.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003917z97bYfNjPBO3ak8R.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016003918PhHTX3flbUFacO6v.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他一些时尚动向：</h3><p>日本运动品牌 ASICS Tiger 与法国人气商店 colette 联手，推出名为<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/asics-tiger-x-colette-yukata\" rel=\"nofollow\"> yukata </a>的鞋款。这款鞋子将于 10 月 22 日正式开售。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016092358kejnVCvmMYNXf1Z5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016092342L65pGmhX4a7Rfdst.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016092353yxrGeNdahBS94olI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>最近去日本的话，不妨去东京国立美术馆的表庆馆看一下<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/cartier-magicien-tokyo-national-museum-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Cartier Magicien </a>的展览。展览将展出 550 件珍宝，其中有 50 件 Magicien 全新作品，还有 55 件 Cartier Tradition 典藏。该展览到 10 月 21 日结束。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610160925310JltCms3erWFVyQ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016092447e9RCNUEFsn35KgoZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016092502vrUm25BcPTY8CJG6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610160925127IxpKwkct8TeEVWs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016092542l9nAHQ2CbsgKmw3r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Emma Stone 穿着 Michael Kors 的条纹毛衫，以短发造型登上了 Vogue 十一月的封面。在这一期的内容里面，Emma 身穿 Gucci，再一次展现了她在电影《La La Land》当中的复古造型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016093820P9smG2jZXF3bkVxl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.402500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610160938288DKsF3cHgIWU671b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016093844NmKEgZOnrvF7s2BW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.406250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}